rComments: I had the pleasure of having André as my Intro au jeu prof. He's delightful. He's very kind and very funny and his classes were always fun to attend. It was a little intimidating for me to take this class in French (I'm anglo), but André was always willing to help me out and his class gave me so much more confidence in performing in French.
André is a great prof for the 4th year directing class : he cares about your vision and is very supportive throughout the semester. Beware of favouritism though!
